/// ARD (Automatic Relevance Determination) over latent axes.
///
/// One independent quadratic ridge penalty per latent axis, with one
/// REML-selectable log-precision per axis. Penalty contribution for axis `j`:
///
/// ```text
///   P_j(t; ρ) = ½ exp(ρ_j) · ‖t[:, j]‖²
/// ```

exec
