It is negative whenever `|x| > delta`, so it is not a PSD `PenaltyOp`. The correct PSD operator must either exclude exact Log Hessians from PSD/logdet treatment or use an explicit positive majorizer such as the IRLS curvature `2 lambda / (delta^2 + x^2)`.

